<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HODLINFO </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/telegram.css">
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-9ndCyUaIbzAi2FUVXJi0CjmCapSmO7SnpJef0486qhLnuZ2cdeRhO02iuK6FUUVM" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-cust navbar-expand-lg">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-logo site-name" href="#">HODLINFO</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
                aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav navbar-end">
                    <li class="nav-item theme-toggle-align">
                        <label class="custom-control teleport-switch">
                            <span class="teleport-switch-control-description material-symbols-outlined">
                                light_mode
                            </span>
                            <input type="checkbox" class="teleport-switch-control-input" checked="">
                            <span class="teleport-switch-control-indicator"></span>
                            <span class="teleport-switch-control-description material-symbols-outlined">
                                dark_mode
                            </span>
                        </label>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="content">
        <h1>Connect To Telegram</h1><br><br>
        <h2>Add bot to your group</h2><br>
        <h3>Manual :</h3>
        <h5>1. Open the telegram app.</h5>
        <h5>2. Open the group you want to add the bot to.</h5>
        <h5>3. Click on add members in group settings.</h5>
        <h5>4. Search @HodlInfoBot and click it.</h5><br><br>
        <h3>Automatic :</h3> 
        <h5>Go to : <a href="https://t.me/HodlInfoBot?startgroup=true" class="link">https://t.me/HodlInfoBot?startgroup=true</a></h5>
        <br><br>
        <h2>Chat with the bot</h2>
        <h3>Manual :</h3>
        <h5>1. Open the telegram app.</h5>
        <h5>2.  Click on new message button.</h5>
        <h5>3. In search bar type HodlInfoBot.</h5>
        <h5>4.  Click on @HodlInfoBot.</h5><br><br>
        <h3>Automatic :</h3> 
        <h5>Go to : <a href="https://t.me/HodlInfoBot" class="link">https://t.me/HodlInfoBot</a></h5>
    </div>

